Digital delivery of music caught up with physical formats like CDs as a money stream last year , the trade association IFPI say on Tuesday .
It came as overall global sales of $ 14.97 billion fell marginally from 2013 .
The report also named the year 's top-selling album sold 10 million copies , while Pharrell Williams ' ` Happy ' was the top single .
Taylor Swift famously removed her music from Spotify .